Home Linux is a multi-user environment so each user is also assigned a specific directory which is

Lib Contains all the shared libraries that are required by system programs.
Media Mount point for removeable media.
Opt contains all the software and add-on packages that are not part of the default installation.

Usr directory contains system files and directories that is shared by all users.
